    <div class="nutri-day"><div class="nd-head quality">DJ</div><div class="nd-body"><div class="nutri-row"><span class="nl">Kcal</span><span class="nv mid">~2.650</span></div><div class="nutri-row"><span class="nl">CHO</span><span class="nv mid">3–4 g/kg</span></div><div class="nutri-row"><span class="nl">Prot.</span><span class="nv hi">151 g ✓</span></div><div class="nd-bar"><div class="nd-bar-fill" style="width:60%; background:#7c3aed"></div></div></div></div>
    <div class="nutri-day"><div class="nd-head preload">DV</div><div class="nd-body"><div class="nutri-row"><span class="nl">Kcal</span><span class="nv mid">~2.600</span></div><div class="nutri-row"><span class="nl">CHO sopar</span><span class="nv mid">extra +</span></div><div class="nutri-row"><span class="nl">Prot.</span><span class="nv">151 g</span></div><div class="nd-bar"><div class="nd-bar-fill" style="width:65%; background:#ca8a04"></div></div></div></div>
    <div class="nutri-day"><div class="nd-head long">DS</div><div class="nd-body"><div class="nutri-row"><span class="nl">Kcal</span><span class="nv hi">~2.950</span></div><div class="nutri-row"><span class="nl">CHO</span><span class="nv hi">5–6 g/kg</span></div><div class="nutri-row"><span class="nl">Prot.</span><span class="nv">151 g</span></div><div class="nd-bar"><div class="nd-bar-fill" style="width:90%; background:#1d4ed8"></div></div></div></div>
    <div class="nutri-day"><div class="nd-head rest">DG</div><div class="nd-body"><div class="nutri-row"><span class="nl">Kcal</span><span class="nv lo">2.450</span></div><div class="nutri-row"><span class="nl">CHO</span><span class="nv lo">2–3 g/kg</span></div><div class="nutri-row"><span class="nl">Prot.</span><span class="nv">151 g</span></div><div class="nd-bar"><div class="nd-bar-fill" style="width:35%; background:#d97706"></div></div></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="info-box">TDEE ~2.950 kcal · Dèficit ~450–500 kcal/dia · Proteïna 1.70 g/kg = 151 g/dia (inclou 2× batut whey 30g) · <strong>Esmorzar diari:</strong> iogurt grec 200g + civada 60g + plàtan + 30g whey (~550 kcal)</div>
